comments: Huerter (ATL) makes hand on ball contact as he blocks Rose (NYK) during his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) momentarily places his hand on Noel's (NYK) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the rebound.
Noel (NYK) makes contact with Bogdanovic's (ATL) arm and affects his control of the ball at the start of his drive.
Noel (NYK) makes marginal contact with Bogdanovic's (ATL) body and does not affect his SQBR.
Randle (NYK) makes contact to Capela's (ATL) arm before any contact with the ball and it causes him to lose possession.
Randle (NYK) gathers the ball and comes to legal jump stop prior to his jump shot attempt.
Bullock (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position on Bogdanovic (ATL) and the contact is marginal.
Capela (ATL) makes incidental contact with Noel's (NYK) foot during the rebound.
Rose (NYK) dislodges Goodwin (ATL) from his position during the rebound.
Collins (ATL) is not established in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Randle (NYK), who moves through the marginal contact and it does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) collapses his arm as he absorbs the incoming contact from Bullock (NYK) during the screen.
Hill (ATL) legally contests Randle's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
